{"title":"Gemini. Linfoma MALT-2025-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/Gemini. Linfoma MALT-2025-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Linfoma MALT (Tejido Linfoide\\NAsociado a Mucosas): Un\\NAnálisis Exhaustivo","guid":"O__iwXacXPlOQORGL420DQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"› A. Definición y\\NCaracterísticas Centrales","guid":"jkGgl5csv_71062sD-Xwhw","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"◊ Nombre formal: Linfoma B Zona Marginal Extraganglionar MALT","guid":"QUezgE0bDsxb702HXQnt3A","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"◊ Subtipo LNH de Células B ★","guid":"58vAi4-f8I8wrUJU0M2lSw","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"◊ Origen: Linfocitos B zona marginal folículos linfoides MALT","guid":"Ey0hwWgSV36MQhWxxhn0Lw","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"◊ MALT: Tejido linfoide asociado a mucosas (GI, resp., ojos, gl. salivales) ★","guid":"x6PolNHT4LdveHbLtvi4FA","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"◊ MALT adquirido: Respuesta a inflamación crónica / autoinmunidad ★","guid":"FD-m8y5eRZdEPSvfOz8CJg","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"◊ Clasificación: Extraganglionar (origen fuera ganglios) ★","guid":"dmgypKMXoo4fxOGncpTe4A","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"◊ Comportamiento: Indolente\\N(crecimiento lento, bajo grado) ★","guid":"QjTBQayUXCyp7hSiIR2i-Q","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"• Implicación: \"Observación y espera\"\\N(watchful waiting) posible ⇄ (Ver V.E)","guid":"3USCMIW7dmMKGgHszCv7Cw","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"◊ Potencial Transformación: LBDCG (Linfoma\\NB Difuso Células Grandes) ★ ⇄ (Ver VI.D)","guid":"3poTd-QlssVtRAMzrNE5bg","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"• Impacto: ↑ Agresividad,\\Ncambio pronóstico/terapia","guid":"2Zz3wKWku6b2oYlC5IvaTw","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"1","text":"◊ Epidemiología:","guid":"Jc50cSS5qqk2DC1s0kTvkA","children":[{"id":"13","pa