común (35-70% MALT)","guid":"yiEWmAi8kWowKY2FH0oXFw","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"• Importancia: Diferenciar de Adenocarcinoma gástrico","guid":"FJ6sb-JqwDbi754O7-OWmQ","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"• Asociación: Helicobacter pylori ⇄ (Ver II.B, V.A)","guid":"QyX02w1il4_m5a5MaONBRA","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"26","text":"◊ No Gástrico: ★","guid":"ETzEoUvQjOm81Ez6CqyeaA","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"• Anexos Oculares (13-15%) ⇄ (Ver II.B, V.G)","guid":"pSaB54WTCexFYlLWd1_owA","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"• Pulmones (9-14%) ⇄ (Ver II.B, V.G)","guid":"I09kJ5Nucl3t1sXc2af0BA","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"• Glándulas Salivales (8-25%) ⇄ (Ver II.A, II.B, V.G)","guid":"WgD8SZy0Vlt6DZr21nvF1g","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"32","text":"• Piel (9%) ⇄ (Ver II.B, V.G)","guid":"GrSmFlez5UbfYY5-3qdC6Q","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"32","text":"• Glándula Tiroides (2-4%) ⇄ (Ver II.A, II.B, V.G)","guid":"BLL8mJMieql4eD3hNoO1kQ","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"32","text":"• Intestinos (delgado/grueso; colorrectal infrecuente) ⇄ (Ver II.B)","guid":"ihGvFJ218IFgztnJvZ_akA","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"32","text":"• Otros (Mama, vejiga, hígado, timo, riñón, próstata)","guid":"cx2yjRsXJp-7fMKOjKWRSA","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"26","text":"◊ Importancia Distinción\\NGástrico/No Gástrico: ★","guid":"u0z1S3yT2c9CHYkoCa_t4Q","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"• Diferencias Etiológicas (H. pylori vs. otros/autoinmunes)","guid":"a_qHrlYChiKhxJZ2CYv9pA","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"• Guía Diagnóstico (Test H. pylori esencial en gástrico) ⇄ (Ver IV.A)","guid":"BFtgiKnqUaMSD0XbkBaJww","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"40","text":"• Guía Tratamiento Inicial (Erradicación H. pylori 1ª línea gástrico temprano) ⇄ (Ver V.A)","guid":"yYxvCxKZbFzw-AemMU0rQg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"0","text":"* II. Etiología y\\NPatogénesis","guid":"8qSuc6olXaiwJYak6VCEWQ","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"› A. Papel Inflamación\\NCrónica y Autoinmunidad ★","guid":"fOm7J4Kd7zEqY6CjvOULPA","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"◊ Mecanismo: Estímulo antigénico sostenido → MALT adquirido\\N→ Proliferación policlonal → Clon monoclonal B (+ alt. genéticas)","guid":"5tuMyhjLX50xI-eDPvIQ7A","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"◊ Asociaciones\\NAutoinmunes\\NEspecíficas: ★","guid":"G_xtjefeOyB3D0XXzKaVXw","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"• Síndrome de Sjögren → Gl. Salivales (Riesgo ↑ 44x) ⇄ (Ver I.C, II.B)","guid":"WtcBswCPjZ0tnTE0JvnEMg","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"• Tiroiditis de Hashimoto → Tiroides (Riesgo ↑ 40-80x) ⇄ (Ver I.C, II.B)","guid":"5ZmIA_9XIqfWPTRuAZZdZQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"45","text":"◊ Modelo Patogénico\\NMultifásico: ★","guid":"z6cQy2eFRSKxNGoo_zhcbA","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"• 1. Respuesta inmune no maligna (policlonal)","guid":"nXL2q0tfxz9zM7a8DInRXw","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"• 2. Expansión clonal dependiente antígeno (Ayuda Células T)","guid":"mV3AeVCFpnd0WIN4t_2DdQ","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"• 3. Linfoma independiente antígeno\\N(Impulsado por eventos genéticos)\\N⇄ (Ver II.C)","guid":"sWodT7snc9wMjbrOWWPrGw","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"• Implicación: Erradicación antígeno (ej. H. pylori)\\Npuede causar regresión en etapa 2 ⇄ (Ver V.A)","guid":"o3dNdQN8m9efogPi2yXMVg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"44","text":"› B. Agentes Infecciosos y\\NAsociaciones Sitio-Específicas ★","guid":"_HF2ZEUBMwq6I48JwQTBUA","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"◊ Mecanismo: Estimulación antigénica crónica","guid":"uj3PMkk8bh2kMznclGQ9PQ","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"◊ Asociaciones\\NClave:","guid":"ZqYfv9X4v-lZYzZs81GZFQ","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Helicobacter pylori → Estómago (Gástrico) (~90-92%) ⇄ (Ver I.C, V.A) ★","guid":"fe3b79GlA5A6paQ9VTtuXw","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"• Chlamydia psittaci → Anexos Oculares (OAML) (Var. geográfica; posible regresión antibióticos) ⇄ (Ver I.C, V.G)","guid":"qHW6u7wyy5ZoAHYaRT_Nxg","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"• Borrelia burgdorferi → Piel (Cutáneo) (Europa endémica; posible regresión antibióticos) ⇄ (Ver I.C, V.G)","guid":"3EjY3PmaQgLZ1GzjGAItKw","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"• Virus Hepatitis C (VHC) → Gástrico, No Gástrico, Bazo (Posible regresión con tto VHC) ⇄ (Ver V.G)","guid":"a2zPG3Y2KcMGB9TPYuvJig","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"57","text":"• Campylobacter jejuni → Intestino Delgado (IPSID) (Mediterráneo)","guid":"QF7xtjJdEIHhf3ZHVBT_lg","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"57","text":"• Achromobacter xylosoxidans → Pulmón","guid":"5Beb6xxiPeKQXH8jZCLQJQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"55","text":"◊ Importancia: Antígeno iniciador determina localización","guid":"Bh_qa5EXGU-BtxZb8aV1Lg","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"55","text":"◊ Limitación: Solo fracción desarrolla linfoma → Factores adicionales necesarios\\N(genética huésped, virulencia, mutaciones B) ★","guid":"3NP9n8tyJFT1wRQSosBLNg","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"44","text":"› C. Patogénesis\\NMolecular ★","guid":"INiOJOtTEU9xMBo34Xt_ag","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"◊ Vía Central: Activación constitutiva NF-κB (promueve supervivencia/proliferación) ★","guid":"OYBw5yBAoUe7-C7xBUdWyQ","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"◊ Translocaciones\\NCromosómicas\\NRecurrentes\\N(Impulsores clave):","guid":"1HuV3pKYSeA7gk9WPlYsww","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"• t(11;18)(q21;q21): BIRC3(API2)-MALT1 (Más común 15-40%; Frecuente pulmón/estómago; Específica MALT; Activa NF-κB; Predice resistencia erradicación H. pylori) ★ ⇄ (Ver IV.C, V. A)","guid":"-b3KvDPm9cUFKrYkk25ufA","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"• t(14;18)(q32;q21): IGH-MALT1 (15-20%; Común ocular, piel, hígado, salival; Activa NF-κB)","guid":"CnC0ggCla6B_hacrl33ANA","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"• t(1;14)(p22;q32): IGH-BCL10 (1-5%; Estómago, pulmón, piel; Activa NF-κB; Resistencia erradicación H. pylori)","guid":"AuNLnYe1Ia_Tl8MoW4rbHg","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"68","text":"• t(3;14)(p14.1;q32): IGH-FOXP1 (<5%; Tiroides, ocular, piel; Posible riesgo transformación)","guid":"sSyveQc1Ry1S97XpcV8vsw","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"66","text":"◊ Otras\\NAlteraciones\\NGenéticas:","guid":"okLi5Tz9iElwsart8Gqq7g","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"• Trisomías (+3, +12, +18) (+3 peor pronóstico?) ⇄ (Ver VI.B Tabla 2)","guid":"pEFmdNBOvLPX_v07NHY-cQ","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"• Del/Mut TNFAIP3 (A20) (Regulador negativo NF-κB; Común ocular, salival, tiroides, hepático; Casos sin translocación) ★","guid":"EKPLv7JWV3JaHsonBWUPwQ","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"• Mut MYD88 (Activa NF-κB; MALT ocular)","guid":"O_WNqx_IIymvowhCy5f1vw","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"66","text":"◊ Convergencia Funcional: Múltiples translocaciones → Activación NF-κB → Crecimiento autónomo ★","guid":"NyeHsQ8oO0WPWuGOzZGhVg","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"66","text":"◊ Especificidad de Sitio: Frecuencia variable translocaciones sugiere influencia sitio/inflamación","guid":"9Ki3LQV25TZJdBrIIYr2Nw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"0","text":"* III.\\NManifestaciones\\NClínicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"› A. Síntomas Generales\\Ny Sitio-Específicos","guid":"7tB9cfuggPfX64FeKfKeoQ","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"◊ Generales: Variables, dependen órgano; Frecuentemente asintomáticos; Linfadenopatía ausente/rara inicio","guid":"75u4GQpsWiwpW4L7Rdhf9w","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"◊ Sitio-Específicos: ★","guid":"Vkehx-HvGIwgqNO47iYttw","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"• Gástrico: Síntomas GI superiores inespecíficos (dispepsia, dolor, náuseas, anorexia, pérdida peso, sangrado/anemia)","guid":"l-q59d5g0T7FmokmqLOusA","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"• Pulmonar: A menudo asintomático (~50%); Tos, disnea, dolor torácico, hemoptisis, inf. recurrentes","guid":"hxcPwJgzcUvH1_2MlikpxA","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"82","text":"• Ocular: \"Parche salmón\" conjuntival, irritación, masa, proptosis, ptosis, diplopía, visión borrosa (a menudo unilateral) ★","guid":"2RUdcryOMKi2FkGw2PbRdA","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"82","text":"• Cutáneo: Pápulas/placas/nódulos rosa/rojo/violáceo (brazos, tronco, cabeza)","guid":"4RaBLQwSfFEtv8IyXd2LyA","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"82","text":"• Gl. Salivales: Masa indolora (parótida, submandibular), posible sequedad (Sjögren) ⇄ (Ver II.A)","guid":"H66PRcZ98oKZreMPX8AleQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"82","text":"• Tiroideo: Masa/bocio rápido crecimiento, síntomas obstructivos, posible hipotiroidismo (Hashimoto) ⇄ (Ver II.A)","guid":"wn6HTeOfb5Fd7nGE0OLYvA","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"82","text":"• Intestinal (no gástrico): Diarrea, dolor, malabsorción, pérdida peso","guid":"_6mbvOnphkWbz2gzNARsGg","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"80","text":"◊ Retraso Diagnóstico: Síntomas inespecíficos imitan condiciones benignas → Alto índice sospecha necesario ★","guid":"cGcy0MTsIoRoi95qucO_cQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"79","text":"› B. Síntomas B\\N(Frecuencia y\\NSignificado)","guid":"fRz6O3J6XvV0gt6o4qH9yg","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"◊ Definición: Fiebre (>38°C), Sudoración nocturna profusa, Pérdida peso (>10%/6m) ★","guid":"WWWPz7UBxDe6cEbLM_3RYg","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"◊ Frecuencia en MALT: Infrecuentes (<5-10%) ★","guid":"5h19CJqU275Co45fBoo7jA","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"◊ Significado: Factor pronóstico adverso; Sugiere enf. avanzada / transformación; Incluido estadificación ('B') ⇄ (Ver VI.B) ★","guid":"nQ8OngPe1AfuaEMmqdUWzQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"0","text":"* IV. Diagnóstico y\\NEstadificación","guid":"F1GPMSEOVxazvK05CSOtaA","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"› A. Procedimientos Diagnósticos\\N(Biopsia, Endoscopia, Imagen)","guid":"cZbo0OuOiLLzVLek04WqGA","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"◊ Biopsia\\N(Piedra\\Nangular): ★","guid":"oPaCeK7yfXwLreSqPskLww","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"• Endoscopia (Gastroscopia, Colonoscopia, Broncoscopia): Elección GI/pulmón (múltiples biopsias, mapeo)","guid":"xV1mzXCjOTZIxBVA3KGqpQ","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"• Guiada por Imagen (TC/Eco): Sitios profundos (salival, pulmón)","guid":"y2tjg1P0Qy-w9JjyFgc0Fw","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"97","text":"• Quirúrgica/Excisional: Piel, masas accesibles (tiroides, salival), conjuntiva","guid":"PV417Ofzborzc5pKr5jcvA","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"96","text":"◊ Imagen\\N(Estadificación):","guid":"rcYNTN2WdNRrWOmYB4Af0w","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"• TC Tórax/Abdomen/Pelvis: Estándar evaluación órganos/ganglios ★","guid":"PZatgm-xFnXK6i3n574frg","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"• PET-TC: Utilidad debatida (captación variable/baja MALT); Útil transformación (ávido FDG) / sitios inesperados;\\NNo obligatoria rutinaria; Selectiva ★","guid":"GIASgXklo64NLWlBcg2Psg","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"• RM: Útil ocular/orbitaria, cerebral, mama, cabeza/cuello","guid":"4X1jb3Jn_LFHzGK8ssf1Ow","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"101","text":"• Ecografía: Sitios superficiales (tiroides, salival, mama, ganglios);\\NEcoendoscopia (EUS) crucial MALT gástrico ★ ⇄ (Ver IV.D)","guid":"mNEqvqpiQIM6U2NpHC-0Nw","children":[]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"96","text":"◊ Laboratorio: Hemograma, bioquímica (LDH, func. hepática), B2-microglobulina, electroforesis proteínas, serologías virales (VHC, VHB, VIH);\\NTest H. pylori (esencial gástrico) ★ ⇄ (Ver I.C, II.B)","guid":"4dGDKeD2YShsbh0_INlfVg","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"95","text":"› B. Histopatología e\\NInmunohistoquímica (IHQ)","guid":"w8NCJbKKtscrjvJfsoHEbA","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"◊ Histología: ★","guid":"IPp8cH01EGkjri0PT3WJYQ","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"• Infiltrado difuso lámina propria (células B pequeñas/medianas, centrocto-like, monocitoides)","guid":"fYjjr4xjJkKvevZzRedULA","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"• Lesiones Linfoepiteliales (LELs): Infiltración/destrucción epitelio (característico) ★","guid":"V2EOjstVD2lpj9c2Nw-K5Q","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"• Colonización Folicular","guid":"ttJTUTXb4iRJ5dNXgfknEg","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"108","text":"• Células transformadas dispersas (sábanas = LBDCG) ⇄ (Ver I.A, VI.D)","guid":"DwyIyJwc8WBRMPqKk5W3FQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"107","text":"◊ IHQ\\N(Inmunofenotipo\\Ntípico): ★","guid":"JcEziD9sP4WmxxryTpownA","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"• Positivo: CD20, CD79a, PAX5, BCL2, CD43 (variable)","guid":"uNdg5v3AbLASJWmh4-du1g","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"• Negativo: CD5, CD10, CD23, Ciclina D1, BCL6 (excluye otros LNH-B)","guid":"bN04II9m-fKb6o7_sEJ2oQ","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"113","text":"• Restricción Cadena Ligera (Kappa/Lambda): Confirma monoclonalidad","guid":"WKOflFHp7K2Jj0JXkstyNQ","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"113","text":"• Ki-67: Bajo (indolente)","guid":"QnjrnHxT3E2P2BdyyWhEww","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"95","text":"› C. Pruebas\\NMoleculares y\\NGenéticas","guid":"fvqfALocxsTt0LddGrjbDA","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"◊ Métodos:","guid":"lJkCrCwwbdNyFHOdb3TkjA","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"• FISH: Detecta translocaciones (t(11; 18), t(14;18), t(1;14), t(3;14)) ★","guid":"-yINZX9HPv2vnPq2McBOHg","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"• PCR (RT-PCR): Detecta transcriptos fusión (API2-MALT1); Reordenamientos IgH (clonalidad)","guid":"RmRWXp3ErmoxSD-mXHGQIg","children":[]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"118","text":"◊ Importancia Clínica: ★","guid":"aWUwv_Wq0ZrleeR8G-t6Rg","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"• t(11;18) en MALT gástrico → Predice NO respuesta erradicación H. pylori → Guía tratamiento ★ ⇄ (Ver II.C, V.A)","guid":"m0WAFeGG-rvgjihYezQ12A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"95","text":"› D. Papel de la Ecoendoscopia\\N(EUS) en MALT Gástrico ★","guid":"1mBHg7wztVBlzT9qooj4GQ","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"◊ Función: Estadificación local precisa (Profundidad invasión pared - T; Ganglios perigástricos - N)","guid":"Yz4atlQkyLSwsvek-jIMAQ","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"124","text":"◊ Valor Predictivo: Profundidad invasión → Predice respuesta erradicación H. pylori (invasión > submucosa = peor respuesta) ★ ⇄ (Ver IV.A, V.A)","guid":"6ogZoG6E87_QPwWlaMA9lQ","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"124","text":"◊ Otros Usos: Diferenciar cáncer gástrico; Guiar biopsias (EUS-PAAF); Seguimiento respuesta","guid":"9LMRr2dvziOQibS0AAhzCw","children":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"95","text":"› E. Indicaciones Biopsia\\NMédula Ósea (BMO)","guid":"fP_HiY76a0uqw_7LZYG5hw","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"◊ Uso Tradicional: Estadificación (detectar Enf. Estadio IV)","guid":"CqAHeQ0jM4t_AXRnpVB5hg","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"◊ Afectación MO en MALT: Infrecuente (~0.5-20%; < gástrico)","guid":"_o0fdBN7fZutTAzxoqBpow","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"128","text":"◊ Necesidad Rutinaria: Debatida; Guías conflictivas; Probablemente no necesaria todos (esp. MALT gástrico temprano HP+ / LZM cutáneo) ★","guid":"poaQVv0BBXUvdfSEGxFKqQ","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"128","text":"◊ Uso Selectivo/Estratificado Riesgo: Reservar casos fallo erradicación, HP-, estadio avanzado, terapia sistémica planificada ★","guid":"ieUurfFSfHxZJuOXDjeUkg","children":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"95","text":"› F. Sistemas de Estadificación\\N(Ann Arbor, Lugano, Específicos\\NGástricos)","guid":"FqV2cK60fc3tWhPtBAswwg","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"◊ Ann Arbor (Modif. Cotswolds): Histórico (Estadios I-IV; E, B, S) ★","guid":"YPbBk0X0XFDZNI271F0bEw","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"◊ Lugano: Recomendado actual; Simplifica (Limitada I/II vs. Avanzada III/IV); Incorpora PET-TC respuesta ★","guid":"XZ7XiOjOnyIPpvfZxB64Og","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"◊ Específicos Gástricos\\N(Capturan invasión mural): ★","guid":"Kzg3n92DSimLgd9Q2OKG0Q","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"• Ann Arbor Modificado Gástrico: IE1 (mucosa/submucosa) vs. IE2 (>submucosa); IIE1 (regional) vs. IIE2 (distante) ★","guid":"vDF5SMO5XxUU4gHi8lJEzQ","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"• TNM (Adaptado / París): T (profundidad), N (ganglios), M (metástasis) ★","guid":"j6efvyDiyi5DPagyDaFyoA","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"136","text":"• Estadificación EUS (Clínica): Descripción invasión mural (mucosa/submucosa, muscular, serosa) ★","guid":"sfpwWHK4iNeLEX0NyoUtVg","children":[]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"133","text":"◊ Relevancia: Ann Arbor/Lugano (sistémico); TNM/EUS (local gástrico - predicción respuesta HP, guía tto local)","guid":"s9ZD_LTwyb0YVNZuG-1Oiw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"0","text":"* V. Opciones de\\NTratamiento ★","guid":"","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"› Dependencia: Sitio (Gástrico/No), Estadio, Síntomas, Infección (H. pylori), Factores paciente","guid":"9njTWZbVWpazFKmCxi6Mfw","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"› A. Tto Linfoma MALT\\NGástrico + H. pylori ★","guid":"Q0pWSK8NL7ZmlzYOUtkhLw","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"◊ 1ª Línea (Localizado I/II1 + HP+): Erradicación H. pylori (Antibióticos + IBP) ★ ⇄ (Ver I.C, II.B, IV.A)","guid":"Ib20vBbfmQsnDvCIxxzt4w","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"◊ Respuesta: Regresión completa ~75-90%; Lenta (meses-1 año+); Confirmar erradicación; Monitorizar (Endoscopia+Bx, EUS)","guid":"-xYlFdBDFh07u7KcElkhEw","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"◊ Factores No\\NRespuesta: ★","guid":"E4L268nEhHswG7vGvKSASA","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"• t(11;18) (predictor más fuerte) ★ ⇄ (Ver II.C, IV.C)","guid":"ZNktIVpdiQwqYUjTbzAjQQ","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"• Invasión profunda pared (EUS > submucosa) ★ ⇄ (Ver IV.D)","guid":"sIGYc8zV5KzgI1VsSvFu7A","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"146","text":"• HP-negativo inicial","guid":"veCI2_oiPtilapRMAxgXBA","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"146","text":"• Transformación LBDCG no detectada ⇄ (Ver VI.D)","guid":"3UzNDkjteKV3nlMP8MtJVA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"141","text":"› B. Radioterapia (RT) ★","guid":"fGevBFpkJyUivmT0aKC8Bg","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"◊ Indicaciones:","guid":"yGYnc2766cB_WrUSaop2jA","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"• MALT Gástrico localizado HP-","guid":"aEQtJ0opRfwshfziIRpUuQ","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"• MALT Gástrico localizado HP+ no respuesta / recaída post-erradicación","guid":"WrX7vr4E0BEH-yeh1-wuWQ","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"• 1ª línea MALT No Gástrico localizado (ocular, tiroides, salival, pulmón, piel)","guid":"223SNcaEa220kbTOx_JROw","children":[]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"151","text":"◊ Técnica: ISRT (Sitio Involucrado); IMRT/VMAT","guid":"JKIM1aJJPhmOfg2eP0Hv3g","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"151","text":"◊ Dosis:","guid":"xE9bO7QVUQkNI5YzVkzCeQ","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"• Moderada: 24 Gy (12-16 fr) - Efectiva y tolerada (opción estándar) ★","guid":"fdwMuPah-y-DAOIAak8t2Q","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"• Tradicional: 30 Gy","guid":"p5EyAipjqc11i2E601HneQ","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"157","text":"• Ultra-baja: 4 Gy (2 fr) - Altas tasas respuesta; posible inicial/paliativo (evaluación ensayos) ★","guid":"3ttDOYcY5HdYXGLSOUooEA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"161","parent":"141","text":"› C. Inmunoterapia y\\NQuimioinmunoterapia ★","guid":"dqD0dnfT3TWS3TG9sKMh9A","children":[{"id":"162","parent":"161","text":"◊ Indicaciones: Enf. Avanzada (III/IV), diseminada, sintomática, voluminosa, progresiva;\\NLocalizados no candidatos / refractarios tto local","guid":"Npdt50uGThl9sZdeAgOTQQ","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"161","text":"◊ Rituximab\\N(Anti-CD20): ★","guid":"1YwrYeGeIPcJl62vOyhlXA","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"• Monoterapia: Opción válida (mayores/frágiles); SC ~ IV","guid":"ENYeTiyM475plXvco_RQzg","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"• Mantenimiento: Prolonga control","guid":"mKc6rbbBuVLJTwhwXDULJQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"161","text":"◊ Quimioinmunoterapia (Rituximab +\\NQuimio): Estándar Avanzada / R-R","guid":"k9q2_huD3gUrkWcvHh2Nmg","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"• BR (Bendamustina + Rituximab): Muy eficaz, altas RC (>80-95%); Preferido a menudo ★","guid":"IjdTMka7LH80SBQnitaU3w","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"• R-Clorambucilo: Oral, menos intensiva","guid":"1FMn8ttpinI9fWIi7uQlLA","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"166","text":"• R-CVP (Ciclofosfamida, Vincristina, Prednisona)","guid":"6KMp5dFBSET2P_zqxYJGTg","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"166","text":"• R-CHOP (con Doxorrubicina): Más intensivo; reservado (sospecha transformación / agresivo)","guid":"Qv7a6kPyWSOAr8sHYXdppg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"141","text":"› D. Terapias Dirigidas y Nuevos\\NAgentes (Principalmente R/R) ★","guid":"Vyp0AU3dc3nbSQ4Lqo76CQ","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"◊ Inhibidores Tirosina\\NKinasa Bruton (BTKi):","guid":"YhMQypuw7d2XDuAYttcfBg","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"• Ibrutinib: Aprobado LZM R/R (ORR 48%, SLP 14m; toxicidad cardíaca/sangrado) ★","guid":"ppv6L5S0YEY3jZtXMnR92A","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"172","text":"• Zanubrutinib: Nueva gen., aprobado LZM R/R (ORR 68%, duradero; mejor seguridad) ★","guid":"mRRDoMgvOOy6nV652gYUGA","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"172","text":"• Otros: Acalabrutinib, Pirtobrutinib","guid":"z82FpIiba3qI0LbKuBaYkA","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"171","text":"◊ Lenalidomida (+/- Rituximab = R²): Inmunomodulador; Actividad LZM R/R (ORR 54-80%, SLP >17m); Opción guías ★","guid":"W95grC4jiasKRUgh6VqzsA","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"171","text":"◊ Inhibidores PI3K: Aprobados indolentes R/R (toxicidad específica)","guid":"QXxtoRSFIt8LSSZnjX_nbw","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"171","text":"◊ Terapia Células CAR-T (Anti-CD19): ★ ⇄ (Ver VII.A)","guid":"YJQIgIe_Ep6fNAs8TiaxDQ","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"• Lisocabtagene maraleucel (Breyanzi): Resultados positivos LZM R/R\\N(Ensayo TRANSCEND FL); Nueva opción muy refractarios ★","guid":"JjckQmIAHxUB1djiFKDlcA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"141","text":"› E. Observación y Espera\\N(\"Watch and Wait\") ★","guid":"gONksN9uSdyBHQwbVM9n4A","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"◊ Indicaciones: Enf. localizada, asintomática, no amenaza órganos. Opción válida y frecuente ★ ⇄ (Ver I.A)","guid":"IvsdTH1a9UnBwUyUNRwFfw","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"180","text":"◊ Inicio Tratamiento: Solo si síntomas, progresión rápida, amenaza función órgano","guid":"pwiAoXJI2r7R4HP1BP4aMg","children":[]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"141","text":"› F. Cirugía","guid":"D8NjRc3lC33QNsPJS_k-WA","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"◊ Papel Limitado: Casos muy seleccionados (localizado resecable); Biopsia excisional curativa; Complicaciones; Esplenectomía (LZME) ★","guid":"dmvKNXEiUJ-Roy16QsgSEw","children":[]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"141","text":"› G. Tratamiento\\NBasado en Sitio\\N(No Gástrico) ★","guid":"726frrKg5qlgezkHFb8RMg","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"◊ Principios Generales: RT localizado; Terapia sistémica avanzado/sintomático","guid":"58HuBRFf36OmOijYtpt__Q","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"◊ Consideraciones\\NEspecíficas:","guid":"o2kO3hxkTVWluEVntbkssw","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"• Ocular: RT (dosis baja/mod/ultra-baja); Antibióticos (si C. psittaci); Rituximab sistémico ⇄ (Ver I.C, II.B)","guid":"8xC2gAucS0RK8TI5LJq9Wg","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"187","text":"• Pulmonar: RT; Cirugía (seleccionados); Terapia sistémica","guid":"kOBWI7KLqLPi-KD2mP3BCA","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"187","text":"• Cutáneo: RT; Antibióticos (si Borrelia); Rituximab (intralesional/sistémico); Quimioinmuno ⇄ (Ver I.C, II.B)","guid":"OqJZogLwqLXzwl0_9IfFzA","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"187","text":"• Salival/Tiroideo: RT localizada; Cirugía (tiroides) ⇄ (Ver I.C, II.A)","guid":"_fZ_srA80tMV2B1AU2B0IA","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"187","text":"• Esplénico (LZME): Esplenectomía, RT bazo, Rituximab (+/- quimio), Tto VHC ⇄ (Ver I.B, II.B)","guid":"pKFOOMTsRNf4KP7xcuKGiQ","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"187","text":"• Ganglionar (LZMG): Manejo similar otros indolentes (BR/R-CVP) ⇄ (Ver I.B)","guid":"U-SdGgEvNzq8I0UDcK8YHA","children":[]}]},{"id":"194","parent":"185","text":"◊ Individualización: Necesaria por heterogeneidad sitios; Sopesar eficacia vs toxicidad","guid":"2i44pJSJHwpid4wFakI8NQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"195","parent":"0","text":"* VI. Pronóstico y\\NSupervivencia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"› A. Pronóstico General y\\NTasas Supervivencia ★","guid":"XEYQLG4DyKndFReiWba76Q","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"◊ General: Favorable, indolente ★","guid":"0VYreoh9rRSCu-ImosMk_A","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"◊ SG 5 años: > 85-90%","guid":"dwKfY35_O6Mojn3y74NjiA","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"196","text":"◊ SG 10 años: ~75-90% (variable)","guid":"n6zL21EoSOWdazNkt2TTLg","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"196","text":"◊ Mortalidad Específica Linfoma: Baja (~4% a 10 años)","guid":"qhLWcjfT3KcQ4W_lyrpPUQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"195","text":"› B. Factores\\NPronósticos ★","guid":"bt0ZoFs8pZhp27rqvJPJxw","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"◊ Clínicos Adversos:","guid":"QexnXvyTb03HRuEgqYqrPg","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"• Edad ≥ 70 años","guid":"C-73YE4aB_g7N7X8hgow0Q","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"• Estadio Ann Arbor III o IV ⇄ (Ver VI.E)","guid":"op01DPPW7r7jtJdigXyJFA","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"202","text":"• LDH sérica elevada","guid":"W_DYS-8JoLc74W4TylkNBg","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"202","text":"• Mal Estado Funcional (ECOG > 1)","guid":"y6R00Rf7L4ejwX9aZnuhBg","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"202","text":"• Síntomas B ⇄ (Ver III.B)","guid":"pv5ccdgh4qU79fguP8AAuA","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"202","text":"• Afectación Ganglionar","guid":"i_vaEFoBckfAYKqXwIJ-tQ","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"202","text":"• Proteína Monoclonal (M-protein)","guid":"6txDZ6HS-2bvc4AR1tq6aw","children":[]}]},{"id":"210","parent":"201","text":"◊ MALT-IPI\\N(Índice Pronóstico\\NIELSG-19): ★","guid":"QqBVSsVl1n7wWcGN5fuGZA","children":[{"id":"211","parent":"210","text":"• Factores: Edad ≥ 70, LDH elevada, Estadio III/IV (1 punto c/u)","guid":"dO5s0OQ_1ir9JksI-WXheA","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"210","text":"• Grupos Riesgo: Bajo (0), Intermedio (1), Alto (≥2)","guid":"y4IiARSKufQctN03vmeBUw","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"210","text":"• Discriminación: SLE, SLP, SG","guid":"6_e-lQMakeEZuFGMFiT0GQ","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"210","text":"• Modificación Propuesta (EMZL-MPI): Añadir Proteína Monoclonal","guid":"g1nhB3xIYn3VzqT-gDiI0Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"215","parent":"195","text":"› C. Riesgo de Recaída y\\NFactores Asociados ★","guid":"8LHfETWzuljUcy1F5QsoYA","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"◊ Ocurrencia: Posible, a veces tardía (~37% global; mediana 47m) ★","guid":"m8ODxDdQn2gRjKhHEx_Irg","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"215","text":"◊ Tipo: Locales o a distancia (más comunes)","guid":"34wNwG_oiutnfYZGL4RNBA","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"215","text":"◊ Sitio: No gástricos > Gástricos (?)","guid":"YjJa5doaLEaxt4N3x_o7QA","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"215","text":"◊ Genética: t(11;18) → Tiempo hasta recaída más largo ★ ⇄ (Ver II.C)","guid":"7PipgL8NTSi65hVIDhYTDw","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"215","text":"◊ Implicación: Observación a largo plazo necesaria ★","guid":"20YDS5yadmzEDYYyYYDlhQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"221","parent":"195","text":"› D. Transformación a\\NLinfoma Agresivo (DLBCL)\\N★ ⇄ (Ver I.A, IV.B, V.A)","guid":"GSUsnkjUL9RlQZP2HAgn1A","children":[{"id":"222","parent":"221","text":"◊ Frecuencia: Infrecuente (<10%) ★","guid":"ZnF-eYe8x8ocUwXEeKgVWg","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"221","text":"◊ Sospecha Clínica: Crecimiento rápido, Síntomas B, ↑↑LDH","guid":"7ah5A2u3fVaLVSMXlYMimQ","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"221","text":"◊ Histología: Linfoma de células B del manto","guid":"28qi6OPebkRiGmVPl6KFrQ","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"221","text":"◊ Impacto: Peor pronóstico; Requiere tto intensivo (ej. R-CHOP) ★","guid":"3-gQhsQV1oPWXHxtBzS69g","children":[]}]},{"id":"226","parent":"195","text":"› E. Impacto Localización y\\NEstadio en Pronóstico","guid":"L_fNvvziBIStonEvMe6M1g","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"◊ Estadio: Avanzado (III/IV) = Factor Adverso Clave ★ ⇄ (Ver VI.B)","guid":"70H5rX2gwXKzP3eaQHEJyg","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"226","text":"◊ Localización: Pronóstico general bueno; Gástrico HP+ localizado excelente; Sitio primario no predictor independiente fuerte ajustado","guid":"w3LafdNHjjJ_YGziRcRJHA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"0","text":"* VII. Investigación\\NActual y Recursos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"› A. Líneas Investigación\\NActivas y Ensayos Clínicos","guid":"oYtKQeS0pVApOjKhmbkPMg","children":[{"id":"231","parent":"230","text":"◊ Comprensión Mo